name: Metamystic Study Guide
description:
"We prefer a more hands-on approach to our teachings. This study guide is actually more of a safety manual."
—Professor Gahf

name: SCRAP 80-T Alchemic Regression Dual-Utility Inter-Nodal Operator
description:
"Yes, it's a rather long name for something so simple, but these have revolutionized the home golem-making industry."
—Researcher Kaii

name: Devourer Egg
description:
These eggs would be perfect source for the next generation of Drottot Lashtail's devourers!
Event Item

name: Sample of Hylek Poison
description: Hylek poison from the Durotl tribe that Blopp needs for his research.

name: Shiny Red Apple
description:
Looks perfect for one of Farmer Eda's pies!
Event Item

name: Blob of Toxin
description:
Apprentice Jameson needs these samples to devise an antitoxin.
Event Item

name: Raven Egg
description: A raven egg that must have fallen out of a roost. Return it to honor Raven.

name: Flame Legion Battle Plans
description: Drawn up by the Flame Legion. This could be invaluable if it were to fall into the right hands.

name: Seraph Badge
description: The badge of a fallen Seraph soldier—Sergeant Rane is collecting these.

name: Piece of Charr Scrap Metal
description: Metal salvaged from Sapper's Delve. Vanguard Scout Holt in Hautclaire Vale might find this useful.

name: Prickleberry
description: These are the berries that Chief Nrocroc is collecting to feed his tribe.

name: Grub Egg
description: The egg of a grub. The Tarstar tribe is known to eat this particular delicacy.

name: Ancient Demetra Tablet
description: This tablet contains a partial history of people and events in ancient Demetra. Take it to the Durmand Priory Explorer to gain renown in the area.

name: Heart of Fire
description: The smoldering heart of an elder imp of fire.

name: Fragment of Earth
description: A small piece of an Earth Elemental. You can feel intense power radiating from it.

name: Burning Ember
description: Holding this mass feels like your hand is on fire.

name: Heart of Darkness
description: The corrupting heart of an elder imp of shadow.

name: Volcanic Earth Elemental Core
description: The core of a volcano-dwelling earth elemental. Ambr's lab wants these for their golem experiments. It looks like three cores will power an inactive golem.

name: Alpha Inquest Control Key
description: The Order of Whispers can use this key to hamper Inquest efforts in this area.

name: Beta Inquest Control Key
description: The Order of Whispers can use this key to hamper Inquest efforts in this area.

name: Grawl Potion
description: Hunter Glynis may find this useful.

name: Piece of Undead
description:
This gruesome limb once belonged to one of Zhaitan's undead minions. The asura harvesting team can use this body part for experiments.
Event Item

name: Inquest Blueprints
description: These are Inquest schematics. Roc'loaka the Tinkerer in Quandry Scratch may have a use for it.

name: Breeze Rider Essence
description: Magical dust from a breezerider. Rixt thinks this is what gives them their ability to fly. He might be interested in this.

name: Encryption Crystal
description: This crystal contains information that will help Frazz gain control of Bauxite Alchemicals faster.

name: Orrian Energy Source
description: This energy source could be the key to something...

name: Harpy Feather
description: A feather plucked from a harpy. Wode might find these useful.

name: Jotun Runestone
description: Albin Chronicler is very interested in these.

name: Blue Wurm Husk
description:
An odd blue wurm husk
<c=@flavor>"This may have come from a Bug!"</c>
